# Shared UI Boundary

- `src/app/shared/ui/` is reserved for Spartan wrappers/primitives and low-level UI directives.
- `src/app/shared/components/` is for reusable app-level components composed from Spartan primitives.
- Do not place app-specific business semantics in `shared/ui`.
- Do not duplicate wrapper components in `shared/components`; consume wrappers from `shared/ui` instead.
- When adding new reusable UI patterns (headers, action footers, row menus), place them in `shared/components`.
